This first part provides an introduction to business analytics, big data, and the application of big data for marketing decisions.  A novel big data and AI driven marketing analytics process model is presented and its step-by-step stages are described in detail.  This new marketing analytics process model forms the foundation of this book.  /n/nChapter 1: Business Analytics for Professionals; 
Chapter 2: Conceptual Framework of Business Analytics; 
Chapter 3: Marketing Analytics for Marketing Decision-Making
